  <brief_title>An Imaging Trial of the Distribution of Topical Gel Formulations in the Human Vagina</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Imaging Trial of the Distribution of Topical Gel Formulations in the Human Vagina: Candidate Formulations</official_title>
  <sponsors>
