  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to assess the distribution and spread of four different vehicle
      formulations in the vagina. In-vivo data will be obtained regarding each vehicle formulation
      at various time points after insertion of the gel into the vagina.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
